episodes.title: Cults/Religion - Jehovah's Witnesses
episodes.description:
Join this weeks episode as we talk about and interview a former Jehovah's Witness. We find out these people are a little more than the annoying bible thumpers that may interrupt your lunch hour. In this episode we expose the dark side of this cult that is a detriment to them and the people around them.
